        <abstract> 
<p>Corrections for <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>. Has sold 6500 copies in England.</p>  
<p>Has finished rough draft of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, but will put it aside for the summer.</p> 
            <p>Will refresh himself with some curious observations on the response of plants to certain stimuli.</p>
